[package]
name = "iroh-gossip"
version = "0.95.0"
edition = "2021"
readme = "README.md"
description = "gossip messages over broadcast trees"
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
authors = ["n0 team"]
repository = "https://github.com/n0-computer/iroh-gossip"
resolver = "2"
rust-version = "1.85"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustdoc-args = ["--cfg", "iroh_docsrs"]

[lib]
crate-type = ["cdylib", "rlib"]

[lints.rust]
missing_debug_implementations = "warn"

[lints.rust.unexpected_cfgs]
level = "warn"
check-cfg = ["cfg(iroh_docsrs)"]

[lints.clippy]
unused-async = "warn"

[dependencies]
blake3 = "1.8"
data-encoding = "2.6.0"
hex = "0.4.3"
indexmap = "2.0"
n0-future = "0.3"
tracing = "0.1"

[dependencies.bytes]
version = "1.7"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.derive_more]
version = "2.0.1"
features = ["add", "debug", "deref", "display", "from", "try_into", "into"]

[dependencies.ed25519-dalek]
version = "3.0.0-pre.1"
features = ["serde", "rand_core"]

[dependencies.iroh-metrics]
version = "0.37"
default-features = false

[dependencies.iroh-base]
version = "0.95"
default-features = false
features = ["key"]

[dependencies.postcard]
version = "1"
default-features = false
features = ["alloc", "use-std", "experimental-derive"]

[dependencies.rand]
version = "0.9.2"
features = ["std_rng"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.164"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.futures-lite]
version = "2.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-concurrency]
version = "7.6.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3.30"
optional = true

[dependencies.iroh]
version = "0.95"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
optional = true
features = ["io-util", "sync"]

[dependencies.tokio-util]
version = "0.7.12"
optional = true
features = ["codec"]

[dependencies.irpc]
version = "0.11.0"
optional = true
default-features = false
features = ["derive", "stream", "spans"]

[dependencies.n0-error]
version = "0.1"
features = ["anyhow"]

[dependencies.quinn]
package = "iroh-quinn"
version = "0.14.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.rand_chacha]
version = "0.9"
optional = true

[dependencies.humantime-serde]
version = "1.1.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4"
features = ["derive"]
optional = true

[dependencies.toml]
version = "0.9.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["env-filter"]
optional = true

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1"
optional = true

[dependencies.rayon]
version = "1.10.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.comfy-table]
version = "7.1.4"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies]
rand_chacha = "0.9"
testresult = "0.4.1"
tracing-test = "0.2.5"
url = "2.4.0"
serde-byte-array = "0.1.2"

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["io-util", "sync", "rt", "macros", "net", "fs"]

[dev-dependencies.clap]
version = "4"
features = ["derive"]

[dev-dependencies.humantime-serde]
version = "1.1.1"

[dev-dependencies.iroh]
version = "0.95"
default-features = false
features = ["metrics", "test-utils"]

[dev-dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.20"
features = ["env-filter"]

[features]
default = ["net", "metrics"]
net = ["dep:irpc", "dep:futures-lite", "dep:iroh", "dep:tokio", "dep:tokio-util", "dep:futures-util", "dep:futures-concurrency"]
rpc = ["dep:irpc", "dep:tokio", "dep:quinn", "irpc/rpc", "irpc/quinn_endpoint_setup"]
test-utils = ["dep:rand_chacha", "dep:humantime-serde"]
simulator = ["test-utils", "dep:tracing-subscriber", "dep:toml", "dep:clap", "dep:serde_json", "dep:rayon", "dep:comfy-table"]
metrics = ["iroh-metrics/metrics"]
examples = ["net"]

[[test]]
name = "sim"
path = "tests/sim.rs"
required-features = ["test-utils"]

[[bin]]
name = "sim"
required-features = ["simulator"]

[[example]]
name = "chat"
required-features = ["examples"]

[[example]]
name = "setup"
required-features = ["examples"]

[profile.bench]
debug = true

[profile.release]
debug = true

[package]
name = "loro"
version = "1.8.1"
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/loro/"
description = "Loro is a high-performance CRDTs framework. Make your app collaborative efforlessly."

keywords = ["crdt", "local-first"]

[dependencies.generic-btree]

[dependencies.tracing]

[dev-dependencies]

anyhow = "1.0.83"
ctor = "0.2"
rand = "0.8.5"
pretty_assertions = "1.4.0"

[dev-dependencies.dev-utils]

[features]

[lints.rust.unexpected_cfgs]
level = "warn"
check-cfg = ["cfg(loom)"]

[package]

version = "0.9.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.20"
features = ["env-filter"]
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.47.1"
features = ["macros", "sync"]

[dependencies.tokio-stream]
version = "0.1.17"
features = ["sync"]

[dev-dependencies]
assert_matches = "1.5.0"

version = "1.47.1"

[dev-dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.20"
